Angola
- Ndalatando. 11 Apr 2018. At least 78 suspected cases recorded in the period 4-9 Apr 2018 in northern Cuanza Norte Province.
http://allafrica.com/stories/201804100784.html

Australia
- Queensland. 11 Apr 2018. The Mackay Public Health Unit said laboratory tests found a Bowen resident had type 2 dengue fever after travelling overseas.
https://www.centraltelegraph.com.au/news/dengue-fever-case-confirmed-in-north-queensland/3384465/

